Subject: File and Folder deletion report/inquiry help
Description: Hi can you assist with the following, a folder and files were deleted from a folder, can you assist in finding out who deleted the files
What_We_Know__c:
1) In SAM, the log file path was configured as:
SBTFileMon_Logs<SERVER_NAME>_Log_.tsv

2) When it should have been configured as:
C:Program FilesStealthbitsStealthAUDITFSACSBTFileMon_Logs<SERVER_NAME>_Log_.tsv
Solution_Comment__c:
The file output in Activity Monitor looked to be malformed. When we added the rest of the path, we were able to see the data coming in as expected and NEA was able to successfully scan. 

SBTFileMon_Logs<SERVER_NAME>_Log_.tsv     to     C:Program FilesStealthbitsStealthAUDITFSACSBTFileMon_Logs<SERVER_NAME>_Log_.tsv

Unfortunately, we did not still have the data for the deletion in question the customer was investigating, however, we have corrected this for future events.
